doesn't make
a great company.

00:37:42,193 --> 00:37:43,795
And your valuation
isn't trivial.

00:37:43,795 --> 00:37:45,263
It's just way too soon
for me.

00:37:45,263 --> 00:37:49,300
I mean, I‐I'm out,
but I‐I think the only person

00:37:49,300 --> 00:37:51,069
