00:41:35,193 --> 00:41:37,295
Right.
How are you gonna get
the other $100,000?

00:41:37,295 --> 00:41:38,596
We have people
who are interested.

00:41:38,596 --> 00:41:39,964
I know I can get
the other $100,000.

00:41:39,964 --> 00:41:41,032
Okay.
I know I can.

00:41:41,032 --> 00:41:43,034
I'll give you $100,000
for 25%,

00:41:43,034 --> 00:41:45,837
