the other $100,000.

00:41:45,837 --> 00:41:47,705
Yeah.

00:41:47,705 --> 00:41:48,706
Done.

00:41:48,706 --> 00:41:50,775
Greiner: Whoo!
[ Laughs ]

00:41:52,110 --> 00:41:53,611
Thank you, Mark.

00:41:53,611 --> 00:41:55,446
You got to work
your ass off, okay?
I will, I will.

00:41:55,446 --> 00:41:56,514
All right.
I really will.

00:41:56,514 --> 00:41:58,116
All right, Alexander.
‐[ Scoffs ]

