Simone: I cannot believe I just
made a deal with Mark Cuban.

00:42:04,288 --> 00:42:06,758
He went out first.
I was so disappointed.

00:42:06,758 --> 00:42:09,694
And he came back in
after listening to everything.

00:42:09,694 --> 00:42:11,963
And this terrible deal
I'm trying to make with Kevin.

00:42:11,963 --> 00:42:14,565
And it was ‐‐ It's ‐‐
This is the best day of my life.

00:42:14,565 --> 00:42:16,300
‐Are you upset?
‐No, not at all.

00:42:16,300 --> 00:42:18,102
I would have never done it
for less than 50%.

00:42:18,102 --> 00:42:20,671
Kevin, you saved $100,000
that you can spend in the...

00:42:20,671 --> 00:42:23,341
Chevaliers du Tastevin!
‐Yay!

00:42:23,341 --> 00:42:24,742
‐Yay!
‐Whoo!

00:42:24,742 --> 00:42:25,777
O'Leary: Cheers.

